	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "When he was expelled from the Senate in 18 (Dio 54.14.3) he was old enough to have a son a senator at that time. So he was probably a senator by 31. (TJC) See Wiseman, NM 214, no. 43.\n" .
